 382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ST PHOTO: NG SOR LUAN Deepanraj Ganesan PublishedFeb 29, 2024, 09:33 PM UpdatedMar 01, 2024, 12:57 AM SINGAPORE -Saiyidah Aisyah received a major boost on her comeback trail when she emerged as the fastest local female rower in the recent national selection trials.\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 672, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ST PHOTO\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 411}, {\"ngram\": \"12:57 AM\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 504}, {\"ngram\": \"a major boost\", \"from\": 541, \"to\": 554}, {\"ngram\": \"her comeback trail\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 576}, {\"ngram\": \"the fastest local female rower\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 627}, {\"ngram\": \"the recent national selection trials\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 35-year-old will now head to the April 19-21 Asian and Oceania Olympic Qualification Regatta in Chungju, South Korea, where she must finish among the top five to earn her ticket to Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 870, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 723, \"end\": 728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Football_Confederation\", \"score\": 0.9986349504159827, \"rank\": 0.0013668576418578414, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Football_Confederation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Football_Confederation\"}, {\"begin\": 733, \"end\": 740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceania_Football_Confederation\", \"score\": 0.9999969974168892, \"rank\": 3.0013321172444765e-06, \"text\": \"Oceania\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceania_Football_Confederation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceania_Football_Confederation\"}, {\"begin\": 774, \"end\": 781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chungju\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1710156888004837e-22, \"text\": \"Chungju\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chungju\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chungju\"}, {\"begin\": 783, \"end\": 794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9998347343507605, \"rank\": 0.00016528645822092694, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 859, \"end\": 869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.254218581322119e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her ticket\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 855}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aisyah had made history as the Republic's first Olympic rower at Rio 2016, but took an indefinite break from competition in end-2017 before deciding to gun for her second Games appearance two months ago.\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 1075, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Aisyah\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 878}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 895}, {\"ngram\": \"the Republic's first Olympic rower\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 933}, {\"ngram\": \"Rio 2016\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 945}, {\"ngram\": \"an indefinite break\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 975}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"her second Games appearance\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1059}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the trials, she faced stiff competition from five rowers, including Joan Poh, whocompeted at the Tokyo Games in 2021.\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1148, \"end\": 1156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joan_Poh\", \"score\": 0.9999910241520336, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Joan Poh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joan_Poh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joan_Poh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the trials\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1090}, {\"ngram\": \"stiff competition\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1119}, {\"ngram\": \"five rowers\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1136}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Recounting the time trials at Pandan Reservoir on Feb 26, Aisyah said: \\\"It did not really get to me until I was on the water.\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1229, \"end\": 1245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pandan_Reservoir\", \"score\": 0.8178249519546956, \"rank\": 0.22275555130692537, \"text\": \"Pandan Reservoir\", \"types\": [\"Q12323\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pandan_Reservoir\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pandan_Reservoir\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time trials\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1225}, {\"ngram\": \"Feb\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1252}, {\"ngram\": \"Aisyah\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was feeling very nervous.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So much so that my heart rate was too high.\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my heart rate\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And during the warmup, I had to take some time to just stop rowing and do some breathing.\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1488, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the warmup\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"some time\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"some breathing\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was tensing up.\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1506, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the start line, I was just telling myself, 'I am already here, so just go and do it and give it your best'.\\\"\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1618, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the start line\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1524}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having been away from the national scene since 2017, Aisyah admitted that she was unaware of what to expect and there was an \\\"anti-climactic\\\" end when national coach Goken Sakamoto announced the results.\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1823, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the national scene\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1660}, {\"ngram\": \"Aisyah\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1679}, {\"ngram\": \"an \\\"anti-climactic\\\" end\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1765}, {\"ngram\": \"national coach Goken Sakamoto\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1800}, {\"ngram\": \"the results\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"There was definitely some doubts because I had no idea what Joan's timing was coming into these trials...\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1941, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some doubts\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1868}, {\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1890}, {\"ngram\": \"Joan's timing\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1909}, {\"ngram\": \"these trials\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 1938}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was just focusing on my goal.\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1973, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my goal\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1972}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Joan and I went out at separate times, so I had no idea what the timings could be.\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 2056, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Joan\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 1978}, {\"ngram\": \"separate times\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2011}, {\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2029}, {\"ngram\": \"the timings\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2046}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After the second time trials, coach Goken announced the timings and said I will represent Singapore at the Olympic selection.\", \"from\": 2058, \"to\": 2184, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2149, \"end\": 2158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6978916620148178e-13, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the second time trials\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2087}, {\"ngram\": \"coach Goken\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2100}, {\"ngram\": \"the timings\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2122}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic selection\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was very strange, because usually I get very emotional about these things.\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2264, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these things\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2263}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I was just so tired.\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By the end of the second trial, I just wanted to get home.\\\"\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2349, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2300}, {\"ngram\": \"the second trial\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2320}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ST understands that Aisyah was at least five seconds quicker than second-placed Poh in each of the two 1,500m time trials.\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2473, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2431, \"end\": 2434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poh_Ling_Yeow\", \"score\": 0.9999997551003916, \"rank\": 2.448990033729345e-07, \"text\": \"Poh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poh_Ling_Yeow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poh_Ling_Yeow\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ST\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2353}, {\"ngram\": \"Aisyah\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2377}, {\"ngram\": \"the two 1,500m time trials\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2472}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If the gap between them had been less than five seconds, additional races would have been required to select the top rower.\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2598, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gap\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2485}, {\"ngram\": \"less than five seconds\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2530}, {\"ngram\": \"additional races\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2548}, {\"ngram\": \"the top rower\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first part of the national trials were on Feb 24, with a 2,000m stationary ergometer rowing test.\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2701, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The first part\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2614}, {\"ngram\": \"the national trials\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2637}, {\"ngram\": \"Feb\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2649}, {\"ngram\": \"a 2,000m stationary ergometer rowing test\", \"from\": 2659, \"to\": 2700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A Singapore Rowing spokesman confirmed that Aisyah was the fastest in both categories.\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2704, \"end\": 2713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6978916620148178e-13, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Aisyah\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2752}, {\"ngram\": \"both categories\", \"from\": 2772, \"to\": 2787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Singapore Rowing declined to reveal the timings, the spokesman said it is \\\"delighted\\\" that Aisyah has \\\"made her first successful step\\\" in the road to qualifying for Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2972, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2796, \"end\": 2805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6978916620148178e-13, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://