ime, energy and you invest all your resources in one thing, you can make things happen.\\\"\", \"from\": 3482, \"to\": 3654, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3545}, {\"ngram\": \"your time\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3569}, {\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 3571, \"to\": 3577}, {\"ngram\": \"all your resources\", \"from\": 3593, \"to\": 3611}, {\"ngram\": \"one thing\", \"from\": 3615, \"to\": 3624}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 3639, \"to\": 3645}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2016, it was at the Tangeum Lake in Chungju, where she had earned a historic Olympic spot by winning the B final of the 2,000m women's single sculls.\", \"from\": 3656, \"to\": 3808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3695, \"end\": 3702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chungju\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1710156888004837e-22, \"text\": \"Chungju\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chungju\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chungju\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Tangeum Lake\", \"from\": 3675, \"to\": 3691}, {\"ngram\": \"a historic Olympic spot\", \"from\": 3725, \"to\": 3748}, {\"ngram\": \"the B final\", \"from\": 3760, \"to\": 3771}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2,000m women's single sculls\", \"from\": 3775, \"to\": 3807}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eight years later, Aisyah will be back at the same venue again, hoping to create another moment to remember.\", \"from\": 3810, \"to\": 3918, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Aisyah\", \"from\": 3829, \"to\": 3835}, {\"ngram\": \"the same venue\", \"from\": 3852, \"to\": 3866}, {\"ngram\": \"another moment\", \"from\": 3891, \"to\": 3905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics 2024 Singapore sports Rowing E-paper Newsletters Podcasts RSS Feed About Us Terms & Conditions Personal Data Protection Notice Need help?\", \"from\": 3920, \"to\": 4076, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3935, \"end\": 3944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S